[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "んしょ、っと……ここは、これで……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00412",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "自分が手伝った錬金術で、できあがった武装……\nどんなのかワクワクしちゃう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00413",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "姉様が使いこなすんだから、どんなものでも\n絶対に素敵。想像しただけで、踊りだしそう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00414",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ちょっとベップ、あんまり期待しすぎないでよ？\nできあがりを見て落胆させたくないからさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00415",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "みんなで作ったんだからガッカリなんてしないよ！\nね、リヒャルト兄さん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00416",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "あれ？　兄さんは？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00417",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "調合を手伝った後、城で別の用件があるって\n帰りましたよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00418",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "そうなんだ。まあいいけど。\nせっかくのアルビーナのお披露目、見てけばいいのに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00419",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "よしっと。\nこ、こんなん出ましたけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00420",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "おおー……さすが姉様、麗しい。\n本当に……あまりの出来に本当に身体が踊っている",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00421",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "えへへ、ありがとう。\nまぁ自分でもいけてるかなって思ってるっすわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00422",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "アルビーナ、一皮むけたみたい！\n大したことできてないけど、私もとっても嬉しい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00423",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "クレオも色々助言してくれたじゃん！\n闘う王女様の着眼点、めっちゃ勉強になったっす！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00424",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "新たな出会いとその協力で完成した、\nあなたの新しい力……見違えたわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00425",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "うん。この武装で心機一転できたらいいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00426",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "かわいいし、機能面も充実してるね？\nとっても動きやすそう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00427",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "はい。これでアタシが思い描いていた\n通りの動きができます。それにこの服なら……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00428",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "……ってことができるっすよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00429",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ほんと！？　すっごい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00430",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "それが本当なら……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00431",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "また、あの暗黒の氷海でだって、\n自信を持って戦えるはず……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00432",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "アルビーナ！！　いるか！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_037_00433",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "あれ、エルスさん……にハイディ？\nど、どうしたの、緊急事態？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00434",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "うん、超緊急事態！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_037_00435",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "頼む……錬金術でタイニーを治してくれ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_037_00436",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]